'''賽夏語文法'''({{lang|en|Saisiyat grammar}})為基於[[賽夏語|賽夏語]]之文法。在文法的分類上[[台灣南島語言|台灣南島語言]]並不同於一般的[[分析語|分析語]]或其它[[综合语|综合语]]裡的動詞、名詞、形容詞、介詞和副詞等之基本[[詞類|詞類]]分類。比如台灣南島語裡普遍沒有副詞，而副詞的概念一般以動詞方式呈現、可稱之為「副動詞」，類之於[[俄语|俄语]]裡的副動詞。<ref>А. А. Реформатский, "Введение в Язковедение", Аспект Пресс--Москва, 1996. ISBN 5-7567-0046-3，ISBN 9785756700466</ref><ref name=diunnbbunhua>張永利,"台灣南島語言語法：語言類型與理論的啟示（Kavalan）"[http://vietnam.nsc.gov.tw/public/Data/012714292271.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://vietnam.nsc.gov.tw/public/Data/012714292271.pdf |date=20131019184617 }}, 語言學門熱門前瞻研究,2010年12月/12卷1期,pp.112-127.</ref> 對於[[数_(语法)|數]]、[[格_(语法)|格]](附著)及[[时态|时态]]改變時[[語詞|語詞]]的變化。賽夏語只有[[代詞|代詞]]本身會依[[格_(语法)|格位]]之不同而進行[[变格|变格]]運作。[[謂語|謂語]]本身不會依[[人称|人称]]、[[数_(语法)|数]]、[[性_(语法)|性]]之變化而進行[[变位|变位]]運作；而是基於[[已然語氣|已然語氣]]及[[非已然語氣|非已然語氣]]、以主事(AF)及非主事(NAF)的觀點結合[[時體氣|時體氣]]語詞(TAM/TMA/動貌詞)，再配合謂語的[[时态|时态]]、[[体_(语法)|体]]、[[语气|式]]進行[[#焦點系統|焦點變換]]來運作。基本的文法分類是將賽夏語詞類之詞綴、字詞結構及分類法，對比[[分析語|分析語]]等之詞類分類法加以條析判別。<ref name=mml>Barbara B.H. Partee, A.G. ter Meulen, R. Wall,"Mathematical Methods in Linguistics (Studies in Linguistics and Philosophy)(語言研究的數學方法)"[http://acl.ldc.upenn.edu/J/J92/J92-1009.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://acl.ldc.upenn.edu/J/J92/J92-1009.pdf |date=20131019185409 }}[http://www.amazon.com/Mathematical-Methods-Linguistics-Studies-Philosophy/dp/9027722455] {{Wayback|url=http://www.amazon.com/Mathematical-Methods-Linguistics-Studies-Philosophy/dp/9027722455 |date=20160307210738 }},Springer,1/e 1993 edition(April 30, 1990). ISBN 9027722455 ，ISBN 978-9027722454</ref><ref name=rmwdixon>R.M.W.Dixon,"The Rise and Fall of Languages(語言的興衰)"[https://www.amazon.com/Rise-Fall-Languages-R-Dixon/dp/0521626544/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1486705612&sr=8-1&keywords=The+Rise+and+Fall+of+Languages] {{Wayback|url=https://www.amazon.com/Rise-Fall-Languages-R-Dixon/dp/0521626544/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1486705612&sr=8-1&keywords=The+Rise+and+Fall+of+Languages |date=20190613230555 }},Cambridge University Press (January 13, 1998). ISBN 978-0521626545 ISBN 0521626544</ref><ref name=pjhectgrammar>Paul J. Hooper,Elizabeth Closs Traugott,"Grammaticalization(語法化/語法化學說)"[https://www.amazon.com/Grammaticalization-Cambridge-Textbooks-Linguistics-Hopper/dp/0521804213/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1486705015&sr=8-1&keywords=grammaticalization] {{Wayback|url=https://www.amazon.com/Grammaticalization-Cambridge-Textbooks-Linguistics-Hopper/dp/0521804213/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1486705015&sr=8-1&keywords=grammaticalization |date=20190613230555 }},Cambridge University Press; 2 edition (August 25, 2003). ISBN 0521804213 ISBN 978-0521804219</ref><ref>,Joan Bybee, Revere Perkins, William Pagliuca,"The Evolution of Grammar: Tense, Aspect, and Modality in the Languages of the World(語法的演化--世界語言的時，體和情態)"[https://www.amazon.com/Evolution-Grammar-Aspect-Modality-Languages/dp/0226086658/ref=sr_1_1?s=electronics&ie=UTF8&qid=1529332864&sr=8-1&keywords=The+Evolution+of+grammar] {{Wayback|url=https://www.amazon.com/Evolution-Grammar-Aspect-Modality-Languages/dp/0226086658/ref=sr_1_1?s=electronics&ie=UTF8&qid=1529332864&sr=8-1&keywords=The+Evolution+of+grammar |date=20190613230555 }},University of Chicago Press; 1 edition (November 15, 1994). ISBN 978-0226086651</ref>

==詞彙與構詞==
{{expand section}}
賽夏語的主要構詞方法有三種：加綴、重疊及複合。

==基本句型及詞序==
雖然賽夏語允許謂語開頭的語序架構(比如：VSO、VOS)，<ref>Li, Paul Jen-kuei. 1998. "台灣南島語言 [The Austronesian Languages of Taiwan]." In Li, Paul Jen-kuei. 2004. Selected Papers on Formosan Languages. Taipei, Taiwan: Institute of Linguistics, Academia Sinica.</ref>，不過賽夏語還是一種主語開頭的語序架構(比如：SVO)之語言，也可以轉為[[主賓格語言|主賓格語言]]，然而，賽夏語仍然有[[部份作格性|部份作格性]](Hsieh & Huang 2006:91)。<ref>葉美利,"賽夏語結構"{{cite web |url=http://thesis.lib.nthu.edu.tw/thesis/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822013409/http://thesis.lib.nthu.edu.tw/thesis/ |archivedate=2013-08-22 }},碩士論文,國立清華大學語言學研究所,76學年度.</ref><ref>"賽夏語的及物性和作格性--基本物句結構和衍伸過程"{{cite web |url=http://thesis.lib.nthu.edu.tw/thesis/archives/GH029744513.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203135238/http://thesis.lib.nthu.edu.tw/thesis/archives/GH029744513.pdf |archivedate=2014-02-03 }}</ref> 除賽夏語外、另有[[巴宰語|巴宰語]]及[[邵語|邵語]]，同為[[北台灣南島語族|北台灣南島語族]]，同樣允許有 SVO 語序架構的[[台灣南島語言|台灣南島語言]]。

